{"tid":402621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上堂咕嚕咕嚕響","createTime":"2017-09-16T14:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T15:15:57.000Z","uid":145395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd82fe643e4d32545bbb60535e786fc05377f10","tid":402621,"uid":145395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:42:26.000Z","msg":"朝早上既都係lecture<br />\n成日遲起身就一鳩沖左反學<br />\n每次一坐低 個肚就不停提我佢未食早餐<br />\n<br />\n多人唔緊要 但靜先攞命<br />\n仲要響到附近都聽到 啲人就陰陰嘴咁笑住同fd講<br />\n冇朋友既我就一個坐向原位繼續咕嚕咕嚕<br />\n越用手咁佢放手就響得大聲d 就好似阿媽打完細路之後個細路一定喊大聲啲咁<br />\n<br />\n響果時重要聽到沖反學後為左補充水份大量灌水啲水即和音<br />\n咕完最後仲送多下高八度既wee聲<br />\n<br />\n個種感覺真係想捐反入老味個窿到"},{"pid":"082961b8daf3f37c0f4daf7bfc6b063ab7f078cb","tid":402621,"uid":145395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打有拎反霸氣既方法"},{"pid":"7d8746aff914ab13bb078d6d5acda9cfbbce15a8","tid":402621,"uid":19072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1714ca922d0bf2c141a360ce663d3a44e2844f8b","tid":402621,"uid":145395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反你老母臭閪</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n臭你又反<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393c51200f8704507a86666a3109401a45467121","tid":402621,"uid":63419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"大把人lecture食早餐<br />\n買個麵包食咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4396b6d789c4c1b44317ff8ee2f58fc4957174","tid":402621,"uid":145395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大把人lecture食早餐<br />\n買個麵包食咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果兩個tutor好mean 有個同學遲左15分鐘 佢叫停佢問左成分鐘 第二個tutor有個偽乾戴帽比佢拮仲要即刻除帽 唔係幾夠膽#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smil